oji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186f3b40476dd227c6775ef24b741d0f43e2d40f","tid":843063,"uid":176657,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T01:29:04.000Z","msg":"幾十歲人都唔化既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n衰一次唔夠 仲要衰多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c764d8713161843d81976a0c739809e98f30ee3","tid":843063,"uid":78349,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T01:35:53.000Z","msg":"原相來自《國家地理雜誌》3月播出的《哥倫比亞機場安全紀錄片》，當中一集內容有關毒犯被海關搜出藏在行李的毒品及被捕過程<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個騙子都幾有誠意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7717c230d87b5b8a892c2f34302b65e3cec688a2","tid":843063,"uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T01:37:04.000Z","msg":"係懲罰佢既智商唔配有咁多流動資金<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949349e46669a5236071f79b61e9c63c95cb8b2c","tid":843063,"uid":103156,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T01:37:41.000Z","msg":"Peter = Erick"},{"pid":"aa85521c6daf9cc09d0fc105f76379e0069c5e82","tid":843063,"uid":110019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T02:40:41.000Z","msg":"係咪都係同一個騙徒嚟架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e2addd633e8d3e16600a35545108bf218a37fb","tid":843063,"uid":81052,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T02:41:45.000Z","msg":"老野就唔好上網"},{"pid":"35aacecb2b4cd3e061c9baa427b15c94c6dd99cc","tid":843063,"uid":6297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T02:42:57.000Z","msg":"早排有位連登手足個老母都話要幫佢個情人"},{"pid":"483ea8ed6d1f467d516747ca67f1ccdd0ab948f5","tid":843063,"uid":166288,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T02:47:15.000Z","msg":"d 啊婆都姣到出汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5288b37785060dec0e7b38fd215aebc5ce0463da","tid":843063,"uid":211579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T02:47:47.000Z","msg":"60歲都聞到棺材浸除啦，仲想性交，屌，on99咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7fe2b1f7661cde525672f24366c23b2dcd181b","tid":843063,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T02:53:20.000Z","msg":"廢老好撚ON9"},{"pid":"b2099742a0f66bc3d1364861f7cef69f5be0028c","tid":843063,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T03:35:29.000Z","msg":"屌，啲圖P到好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a9b6113de3b037284967b2839e514969113c042","tid":843063,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"093300da458a8d24baec2ff7dac03db1f5fe935d","tid":843063,"uid":21917,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T00:21:52.000Z","msg":"改到咁撚假都信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T05:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}